#achievement system

1. 'killed' ships -> points, new user ship
2. bonuses : 
	time slower - slows enemy ships
	double killer - kills two ships with one word
	invincible - makes user ship unkillable
	ice cube - freezes one-two enemy ships
	scissors - makes each word shorter
	health - adds health
	clon - *2p-game* doubles user ships which goes to enemy screen
	booster - doubles speed of user ships
3. achievements
	speedstor - 10 symbols in 1-2 secs
	unstoppable - 10 ships in a row with no hurt	

//each ship's word = 5-9 symbols.
//each bullet's word = 2-3 symbols